Programming Languages and their Uses:

- Python - AI,ML,Data Science
- Java - Android Apps, Desktop Apps
- C - OS, System-level programming
- C++ - Game Development, Desktop Softwares
- JavaScript - Websites, Web Apps
- C#(C Sharp) - Game Development(Unity), Windows Apps
- PHP(Hypertext Pre Processor) - Web development, server-side scripting
- SQL(Structured Query Language) - Databases
- HTML(Hyper Text Markup Language) - Creates the structure of web pages
- CSS(Cascading Style Sheets) - Adds style and design to HTML
